{"word":"H2425 - חָיַי - châyay - khaw-yah'-ee - Live","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָיַי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châyay"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-yah'-ee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Live"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உயிர்பிழை, உயிரோடிரு, பிழை, பிழைத்திரு, பிழைக்கப்பண்ணு ஜீவனோடிரு. வாழ்க, திரும்பிவா, ஜீவித்திரு, ஜீவனம் பண்ணு, உயிரடை, பழுதுபார், வளர், செழி, நீங்கு, வாழ், உண்டாகு உயிரோடுவை ஜீவி, பிராணனைக் காப்பாற்று, உயிர்ப்பி, உயிரோடே காப்பாற்று, வயதாதல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to live, to have life, to remain alive, to sustain life, to live prosperously, to live forever, to be quickened, to be alive, to be restored to life or health"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to live"},{"paragraph":"a) to have life"},{"paragraph":"b) to continue in life, to remain alive"},{"paragraph":"c) to sustain life, to live on or upon"},{"paragraph":"d to live (prosperously)"},{"paragraph":"2) to revive, to be quickened"},{"paragraph":"a) from sickness"},{"paragraph":"b) from discouragement"},{"paragraph":"e) from faintness"},{"paragraph":"d) from death"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to preserve alive, to let live"},{"paragraph":"2) to give life"},{"paragraph":"3) to quicken, to revive, to refresh"},{"paragraph":"a) to restore to life"},{"paragraph":"b) to cause to grow"},{"paragraph":"c) to restore"},{"paragraph":"d) to revive"},{"paragraph":"c) Hiph)"},{"paragraph":"1) to preserve alive, to let live"},{"paragraph":"2) to quicken, to revive"},{"paragraph":"a) to restore (to health)"},{"paragraph":"b) to revive"},{"paragraph":"c) to restore to life"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root (compare <a href=\"#/H2421 - חָיָה - châyâh - khaw-yaw'/2421\">H2421</a>); to <i>live</i>; causatively to <i>revive: - </i>live, save life."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2416 - חַי - chay - khah'-ee/2416\">H2416</a>, <a href=\"#/H2419 - חִיאֵל - Chîyʼêl - khee-ale'/2419\">H2419</a>, <a href=\"#/H2421 - חָיָה - châyâh - khaw-yaw'/2421\">H2421</a>, <a href=\"#/H2422 - חָיֶה - châyeh - khaw-yeh'/2422\">H2422</a>, <a href=\"#/H2424 - חַיּוּת - chayûwth - khah-yooth'/2424\">H2424</a>, <a href=\"#/H2425 - חָיַי - châyay - khaw-yah'-ee/2425\">H2425</a>, <a href=\"#/H3171 - יְחִיאֵל - Yᵉchîyʼêl - yekh-ee-ale'/3171\">H3171</a>, <a href=\"#/H3172 - יְחִיאֵלִי - Yᵉchîyʼêlîy - yekh-ee-ay-lee'/3172\">H3172</a>, <a href=\"#/H3174 - יְחִיָּה - Yᵉchîyâh - yekh-ee-yaw'/3174\">H3174</a>, <a href=\"#/H4241 - מִחְיָה - michyâh - mikh-yaw'/4241\">H4241</a>"}]}